## ğŸ§ª Examples

**Estimate Depth Only:**

```python
from deepfake_classifier import estimate_depth
estimate_depth("data/", "depth/")
```

**Augment Images Only:**

```python
from deepfake_classifier import augment_images
augment_images("depth/deepfake", "processed/deepfake", 3)
```

